    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>Tank Install Calculator does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal information or user data.</p>

    <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>No personal information (name, email, phone)</li>
        <li>No location data</li>
        <li>No usage analytics or statistics</li>
        <li>No advertising identifiers</li>
        <li>No device information</li>
        <li>No crash reports sent to us</li>
        <li>No calculation data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How the App Works</h2>
    <p>All calculations are performed locally on your iPhone or iPad. Your excavation dimensions, tank sizes, and cost estimates never leave your device. We don't have servers to store your data because we don't collect any data.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This app does not use any third-party analytics tools, advertising networks, or tracking services. There are no third-party SDKs that collect data.</p>

    <h2>Sharing Feature</h2>
    <p>When you use the Share button, you control where your calculation results go. The app uses the native iOS share sheet. We don't see or store what you share.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>This app is safe for all ages. We don't collect data from anyone, including children under 13.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>If we ever change this privacy policy, we will post the new version here with an updated date. Since we don't collect your email, we can't notify you directly, so please check back occasionally.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Since we don't collect any data, there's no data to access, delete, or modify. Your privacy is completely protected by design.</p>

